  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es greeſſichu ſawu Rohku pretti tew/ un notihri- fchu taawus Sahrkus itt tchſih- ſti/ un atreinschu wiſſu tawu Alwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es atdoḥſchu tew ta- wus Sohgus ka pirmak/ un ta- wus Padohma-Dewejuß ka pirmgallā. Pehz to tapſi tu no- faukts weens Pitsfahts tahs Taifnibas/ weens peetizzigajs Pilſtahts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ziana taps zaur Teeſu iſpeſtita/ un wiſſas Zeetumnee- ki zaur Taifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tee Pahrkahpaji un Grehzineeki taps koḫpa ſadauſi- ti/ un kas no ta KUNGĀ at- akahpj/ tee ees behjā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tee taps Kauna ta Obsolu deht/ ko juhs bijat eekah- rojuſchi/ un juhs tapſeet neewati to Darsu deht/ ko juhs bijat iſ- redſejſcht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo juhs buhſeet itt ka weens Ohiols/ ka Lappas no- burſt/ un ka Dahrs/ kam uhdens newa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhſ tas Stiprume ka Pakkulas/ un wiſſa Darri- tajs ka Dſirkſtele/ un tee abber taps koḫpa dedſinati/ un ne- weens buhſ/ kas iſdſetſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Chis irr)tas Wahrdṣ ko Jesajus Aimoz Dehls irr redſejs/ pah Juhdu nn Jerusalemi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notiks pastard Pat kā/ tad buhṣ tas Kalns ta Dee- wa Namna ſtiprinahtṣ us to Kalno Wirṣ-Gallu/ un tapṣ pahr teem Pakalneeni pa-aug- ſtinahtṣ/ un wiſſi Pagaxi us winnu tezzehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un daudṣ Tautaṣ ees un fazzthṣ: Eima/ kahtſim us ta KUNGĀ Kalnu/ nṣ to Nammu ta Deewa Jehkaba/ ka wiſch mums mahza taawus Zelttus/ un ka mehṣ ſtaigaht warram winna Tekkaṣ/ jo no Zianas iſees ta Baustiba/ un ta KUNGĀ Wahrdṣ no Jeruſalemēs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſch teefahṣ ſtarp teem Paganeem/ un pahrmah- ſihs daudṣ Landis/ un tee ſakals ſawus Sohbinuṣ par Lemine- ſcheem/ un ſawus Schkehpuṣ par Zirpeem. Jo Tauta prett Tautu nekahdu Sohbinu pa- zels/ un ne mahziſees wairs Karru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Natz tu Jehkaba Namṣ/ ſtaigaſim eekſch ta KUNGĀ Gatsinas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tu effi taawuṣ Landis to Jehkaba Nammu atſahjis/ jo tee irr pilli (Besdeewibas) wairak neka tee Auſtruma Lau- dis/ un irr Laika-Zeenitaji itt ka tee Wiſſteri/ un pee to Swe- fhineeku Behrneem irr winneem Lab-Patiſſhana.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
